  "description": "In this email I\u0026rsquo;m going to, superficially, talk about Barnabus, a piece of software I\u0026rsquo;m working on. But mostly it\u0026rsquo;s going to be, as a lot of writing is, about culture, philosophy, and how those intersect with our ways of living.\n(Note: this email is also the first piece of writing I\u0026rsquo;m drafting while using HashUp, and hopefully will be the first rendered through Barnabus. There might be issues with how it renders, especially since I\u0026rsquo;ll end up having to copy-paste it into Substack to send it to y\u0026rsquo;all.)\n",
